Package: ewgroup
Title: Exponentially Weighted Grouped-Heterogeneity Estimator
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Manu", "Navjeevan", email = "mnavjeevan@tamu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Denis", "Chetverikov", role = "aut"),
    person("Andrei", "Voronin", role = "aut")
  )
Author: Manu Navjeevan [aut, cre],
  Denis Chetverikov [aut],
  Andrei Voronin [aut]
Maintainer: Manu Navjeevan <mnavjeevan@tamu.edu>
Description: Implements an exponentially weighted estimator for grouped
    heterogeneity in collections of noisy cell-specific estimates. The estimator
    pools nearby preliminary estimates using covariance-adjusted exponential
    weights and combines the pooled estimator with the naive estimator using a
    feasible Stein unbiased risk estimate.
